
            Video
            Thai labourers in Israel tell of harrowing conditions
            A year-long BBC investigation has discovered widespread abuse of Thai nationals living and working in Israel - under a scheme organised by the two governments. Many are subjected to unsafe working practices and squalid, unsanitary living conditions. Some are overworked, others underpaid and there are dozens of unexplained deaths.
                
                        23 Nov 2018
                    
                
        
